725828f-a.title: Queens: 121st Street - 18th Avenue
725828f-a.text:
121st Street, north from and across 18th Avenue. The
corner house (left) is the Coluwbian and is the headcuarters
of the Point View Denocratic Club.
P. L. Sperr  March 16, 1932

725827f-a.title: Queens: 121st Street - 18th Avenue
725827f-a.text:
18-38 121st Street, east side, between 18th and 20th
Avenues, showing an old home.
P. L. Sperr  March 15, 1932
